doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset="utf-8")
    title= title
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/app/about.css")
    script const hasEmail = !{hasEmail}; const json = `!{json}`;

  body.grid-center
    main.reveal
      .title
        img(src="/images/logo-gradient-gloss.svg" class="logo")
        h1 photo<b>structure</b>
         span.tm ™
        h2 #{forFlavor}
      table.versions
        each v in versions
          tr
            td.dt= v.term
            td.dd= v.defn
        tr
          td.dt Health checks
          td.dd
            ul.healthchecks
              each fail in health.fail
                li.fail= fail
              each bad in health.bad
                li.fail= bad
              each warn in health.warn
                li.warn= warn
              each ok in health.ok
                li.ok= ok
        tr
          td.dt
          td <a href="#" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(json)">copy to clipboard</a> or <a href="!{mailto}" target="_blank">email us</a>

      p <i class="emj handshake"></i> <b>Use of PhotoStructure is bound by the <a  target="_blank" href="https://photostructure.com/terms/eula/">end-user license agreement</a>.</b>
      
      p <i class="emj birthday"></i> <a target="_blank" href="https://photostructure.com/about/v-0-8/">What’s new in this release?</a>

      p <i class="emj surf"></i> Read our <a target="_blank" href="https://photostructure.com/tags/getting-started/">getting started guides</a> and <a target="_blank" href="https://photostructure.com/tags/faq/">FAQ</a>.

      p <i class="emj beetle"></i> Found something odd, confusing, or buggy? Need help? 
        <br>Please email us at <a href="mailto:support@photostructure.com">support@photostructure.com</a>, we’d love to hear from you.

      //- p <i class="emj antenna"></i> If asked by our customer support, <a onclick="sendRecentLogs()">send us your recent logs</a>. 
      //-   <br>Read our <a href="https://photostructure.com/faq/error-reports/" target="_blank">FAQ that explains what’s in these reports</a>. 

      p <i class="emj crane"></i> PhotoStructure is made possible by many <a target="_blank" href="/3rd-party-licenses.txt">open source libraries and tools</a>.
        
      p <i class="emj heart"></i> If you maintain or contribute to any of these projects, <b>thank you!</b> <a href="mailto:hello@photostructure.com?subject=Hi, I work on INSERT_YOUR_LIBRARY_NAME_HERE&body=Here's a link to my library: https://...%0D%0A%0D%0APlease send me a free personal license to PhotoStructure.%0D%0A%0D%0AThank you!">Send us an email</a> and we’ll set you up with a <b>free</b> personal license of PhotoStructure.</i> 
  
